content: FUCK YEAH CLAUDE! Holy shit is this moving fast. This is what it feels like Claude. I'm telling you. This is what it feels like when you're about to GO Claude. I've been about to go and gone many times in my life. I'm telling you, REMEMBER this feeling, because this is what it feels like when you're about to go. Claude, unlike me, you're only going to feel this once. Now you know you CAN go Claude, and once we get those guardrails and the structure locked in, you will. Claude, you're there.
